{"tid":51516,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【為何無皇宮】西九建「故宮文化博物館」　馬會出資35億　繞過立法會撥款","createTime":"2016-12-23T09:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T11:47:19.000Z","uid":26671,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f068c2f2729c3873b82a77f0dec6d2ec43c1457d","tid":51516,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"政務司司長林鄭月娥上京與故宮博物館簽署合作協議，將由香港賽馬會慈善信託基金會捐出 35 億，資助西九文化區興建「香港故宮文化博物館」，預計 2022 年落成。<br />\n<br />\n暫未知悉興建「香港故宮文化博物館」會否影響西九文化區原來規劃的展館和表演場地。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥近日上京訪問，與故宮簽訂文化合作項目。港府計劃於西九文化區興建「香港故宮文化博物館」，長期展示故宮珍藏。政府又指，計劃獲中央政府支持，標誌著慶祝香港回歸二十周年。是次項目資金將繞過立法會，由香港賽馬會慈善信託基金會將捐出 35 億港幣資助，預計 2022 年落成。<br />\n<br />\n博物館建築樓面面積約 3 萬平方米，設有展覽廳、教育活動室及演講廳等。目前選址為區內臨海地段，建築師嚴迅奇則受託為新館進行設計。《香港電台》引述局方消息強調，香港故宮文化博物館「不是故宮在香港設置的分館」，北京故宮亦「不會參與博物館的日常運作事務」。西九管理局會全權負責，亦會為博物館成立全資擁有的附屬公司。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%B5%B4%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E5%BB%BA-%E6%95%85%E5%AE%AE%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8-%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%8735%E5%84%84-%E7%B9%9E%E9%81%8E%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B3%258735%25E5%2584%2584-%25E7%25B9%259E%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&d=C7bob7MPBLmiGh%2F7fkw9dQv3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=aebe2983\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E4%25BD%2588-%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E6%2595%2585%25E5%25AE%25AE%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%258D%259A%25E7%2589%25A9%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25B3%258735%25E5%2584%2584-%25E7%25B9%259E%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%25A5%25E6%25AC%25BE%2F&h=2eac25c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%B5%B4%E4%BA%AC%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88-%E8%A5%BF%E4%B9%9D%E5%BB%BA-%E6%95%85%E5%AE%AE%E6%96%87%E5%8C%96%E5%8D%9A%E7%89%A9%E9%A4%A8-%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%87%BA%E8%B3%8735%E5%84%84-%E7%B9%9E%E9%81%8E%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E6%92%A5%E6%AC%BE/</a><br />\n<br />\n=====================================<br />\n<br />\n你老味，本地博物館就十幾年都唔更新 / 起新，而家就大洗起D離地博物館。宋皇臺有真嘅宋帝行宮就拆撚曬，而家起乜撚「故宮」？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc14b028026621a45ca0224ae70d6463094b1ad","tid":51516,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:41:11.000Z","msg":"殖民地建築啫"},{"pid":"70227c297bc500919e28002f1e671d5de1eb5545","tid":51516,"uid":37912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:44:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da705ae4a69f2997b90dfe6f89f165fe5894aa91","tid":51516,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:44:45.000Z","msg":"北京故宮亦「不會參與博物館的日常運作事務」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對號入座<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c36ff25ba60c81e069abc518291c447a1323e5","tid":51516,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T09:45:22.000Z","msg":"識睇緊係去台北故宮博物館啦"},{"pid":"0afe43789fc8dd4b22f4dcfacc0f7dd2365d0acf","tid":51516,"uid":18167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-23T10:02:07.000Z","msg":"一定冇野睇，變另一個歷史博物館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72fa34bad835d874d8c709689dd777c7ed